<item>
            <title>[LU-15283] The quota reint thread maybe dead lock with lquota_wb thread</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15283</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The quota reint thread will travel the quota file through iam.  It will hold the dynlock then start a transaction.  The lquota_wb thread will process the update record while reint running. It will start the a transaction then try to acquire dynlock. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
